        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This ice-blue half-mask is adorned with a wicked silver grin that covers the wearer's mouth, leaving the rest of the face uncovered. You gain a +3 item bonus to Intimidation checks.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">2 </span>envision, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The mask emits a soul-chilling scream that deals [[/r 8d10]] negative damage to each living creature in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:40] (<span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"41\" data-pf2-traits=\"auditory,magical,necromancy,negative\" data-pf2-label=\"Greater Mask of the Banshee DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Fortitude</span> save).</p>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply a casting of <em>wail of the banshee</em>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+3 item bonus to Intimidation checks</li>\n</ul>"
